    slug: "real-cost-of-hubspot-crm-vs-salesforce-scale-2026",
    title: "Pipedrive vs HubSpot vs Salesforce: Which CRM Scales Best for Growing Teams in 2026?",
    date: "May 1, 2026",
    excerpt: "Choosing the wrong CRM at 20 people means a painful migration at 100. Here's how Pipedrive, HubSpot, and Salesforce actually compare when your team starts to grow.",
